802
00:51:41,112 --> 00:51:42,672
She's got quite a backbone.

803
00:51:44,312 --> 00:51:46,482
If you're finished, I'll be going now.

804
00:51:50,352 --> 00:51:51,822
Fine. Then listen to what I really have to say.

805
00:51:56,752 --> 00:51:57,762
Go ahead.

806
00:52:00,562 --> 00:52:01,692
Seong Jae's first marriage.

807
00:52:02,662 --> 00:52:04,502
Seong Jae's father forced him to get a divorce.

808
00:52:05,602 --> 00:52:06,862
Even though they were already legally married.

809
00:52:08,232 --> 00:52:11,142
For the heir of a conglomerate, marriage isn't a personal matter.

810
00:52:11,542 --> 00:52:13,872
It's a business arrangement with a family that aids the company.

811
00:52:21,652 --> 00:52:24,822
Seong Jae's father will never give up on him.

812
00:52:25,822 --> 00:52:30,322
I know. That's why I stepped in now, before you both get hurt even more.

813
00:52:31,192 --> 00:52:34,292
As his mother, it would be easier on my Seong Jae...

814
00:52:34,962 --> 00:52:37,032
if you were the one to end things.

815
00:52:37,762 --> 00:52:40,162
Do you understand me?

816
00:52:40,632 --> 00:52:42,432
I understand what you mean.

817
00:52:44,642 --> 00:52:46,142
Please, be realistic.

818
00:52:47,042 --> 00:52:50,842
Chairman Park will stop at nothing when it comes to Seong Jae.

819
00:52:52,212 --> 00:52:53,712
It won't just be you.

820
00:52:55,182 --> 00:52:57,082
Your family will be in danger, too.

821
00:53:03,692 --> 00:53:06,522
If you truly love Seong Jae, let him go.

822
00:53:08,062 --> 00:53:09,432
Because of your relationship with him,

823
00:53:09,862 --> 00:53:11,802
