824
00:53:13,032 --> 00:53:15,672
Do you want Seong Jae to lose everything?

825
00:53:18,542 --> 00:53:19,942
Because true love means...

826
00:53:20,802 --> 00:53:22,712
wanting the other person to be happy.

827
00:53:25,082 --> 00:53:26,512
Please, make the right decision.

