880
00:56:33,662 --> 00:56:34,702
Understood.

881
00:56:39,542 --> 00:56:41,472
I'm dying to see Su Bin.

882
00:56:52,552 --> 00:56:55,992
If I leave all this food out, he'll help himself, I'm sure.

883
00:56:56,652 --> 00:56:57,652
All set.

884
00:57:02,892 --> 00:57:03,892
Right.

885
00:57:06,132 --> 00:57:07,132
What?

886
00:57:09,602 --> 00:57:10,702
Cheol Min.

887
00:57:11,002 --> 00:57:13,242
Could you sort the meeting minutes for me?

888
00:57:13,842 --> 00:57:14,842
Sure.

889
00:57:28,392 --> 00:57:30,152
I was just about to head out. What's up?

890
00:57:32,022 --> 00:57:33,622
Can we talk for a minute?

891
00:57:36,392 --> 00:57:38,262
But I really have to get going right now.

892
00:57:38,562 --> 00:57:41,532
- I just came back to get my phone. - I make you uncomfortable, right?

893
00:57:43,332 --> 00:57:46,102
Showing up right after your surgery when you couldn't even move,

894
00:57:47,242 --> 00:57:48,772
hanging around your hospital room,

895
00:57:50,572 --> 00:57:52,342
telling you I can't give up on you,

896
00:57:53,812 --> 00:57:54,882
and now...

897
00:57:55,982 --> 00:57:57,482
asking you to join my company.

898
00:58:01,122 --> 00:58:04,192
Why are you saying all this all of a sudden?

899
00:58:04,722 --> 00:58:06,792
There's something I've been meaning to tell you,

900
00:58:08,432 --> 00:58:09,532
and I'm going to say it now.

901
00:58:14,162 --> 00:58:15,732
I've been a real jerk.

902
00:58:19,202 --> 00:58:20,372
Eun Oh, I...

903
00:58:21,672 --> 00:58:23,912
When I decided to marry Jung Bo A,

904
00:58:25,582 --> 00:58:28,052
I truly thought it was a win-win marriage.

905
00:58:30,182 --> 00:58:32,252
She had what I lacked,

906
00:58:33,652 --> 00:58:35,092
and she needed me.

907
00:58:37,152 --> 00:58:40,822
So I truly believed I wasn't doing anything wrong.

908
00:58:46,132 --> 00:58:47,802
I know that's what you thought.

909
00:58:49,202 --> 00:58:50,202
But...

910
00:58:50,732 --> 00:58:53,842
- why are you saying this now? - But I overlooked something.

911
00:58:56,172 --> 00:58:57,372
The fact that Jung Bo A was still...

912
00:58:58,942 --> 00:59:00,782
in love with another man.

913
00:59:04,212 --> 00:59:05,852
And even though I knew all that,

914
00:59:07,552 --> 00:59:09,022
I was still going to marry her.

915
00:59:11,522 --> 00:59:13,292
A real jerk who was just in it for the money.

916
00:59:14,962 --> 00:59:15,962
That was me.

917
00:59:20,562 --> 00:59:22,002
And you're only just now realizing that?

918
00:59:22,172 --> 00:59:24,232
So I can only imagine how much you must've despised me.

919
00:59:26,072 --> 00:59:27,972
And yet, I showed up at your cafe...

920
00:59:27,972 --> 00:59:30,242
trying to come back and bothering you.

921
00:59:32,742 --> 00:59:33,742
In the process...

922
00:59:36,212 --> 00:59:37,512
I ended up falling for you.

923
00:59:44,862 --> 00:59:45,922
As for that,

924
00:59:47,022 --> 00:59:49,262
I already gave you my answer back then.

925
00:59:50,832 --> 00:59:52,332
You're just pathetic.

926
00:59:52,832 --> 00:59:54,702
What's the point of you liking me now?

927
00:59:55,232 --> 00:59:58,172
It's all pointless now. That kind of person...

928
00:59:58,872 --> 00:59:59,902
I can't stand them.

929
00:59:59,902 --> 01:00:02,212
Someone who would marry without love for money...

930
01:00:02,272 --> 01:00:04,072
I despise people like that.

931
01:00:07,282 --> 01:00:08,312
You did.

932
01:00:10,012 --> 01:00:12,922
That our values are too different,

933
01:00:13,722 --> 01:00:15,222
